274
00:16:52,361 --> 00:16:55,161
Nagisa must've panicked.

275
00:16:56,661 --> 00:16:58,661
Calm down, Nagisa.

276
00:16:59,761 --> 00:17:01,861
We have three more minutes.

277
00:17:07,361 --> 00:17:09,661
We need to film the real thing.

278
00:17:11,161 --> 00:17:13,760
You're late, Yuri.

279
00:17:13,761 --> 00:17:15,461
She won't make it in time.

280
00:17:17,861 --> 00:17:21,560
Yuri! I'm glad you made it.

281
00:17:21,561 --> 00:17:23,861
Quickly, the Tears of Borgia.

