Yuri had no time to explain,

286
00:17:35,261 --> 00:17:38,061
and Nagisa had a 40 degree fever.

287
00:18:05,461 --> 00:18:10,260
Yuri tried to get as far away from the location as she could

288
00:18:10,261 --> 00:18:12,860
so Nagisa wouldn't be blamed,

289
00:18:12,861 --> 00:18:18,661
and so the fake Tears of Borgia wouldn't appear in the drama.

290
00:18:27,761 --> 00:18:32,360
At the studio, the stand-in maid stabbed Red Hood to death.

291
00:18:32,361 --> 00:18:35,561
All that remained was Nagisa's final shot.

292
00:18:37,161 --> 00:18:40,560
Nagisa, the real jewel won't make it in time.

293
00:18:40,561 --> 00:18:45,060
I'm sorry, but you'll have to wear the fake ring.

294
00:18:45,061 --> 00:18:46,961
I... I understand.

295
00:18:53,361 --> 00:18:55,761
I...

296
00:19:01,061 --> 00:19:02,460
I...

297
00:19:02,461 --> 00:19:04,661
I killed him!

298
00:19:10,561 --> 00:19:12,461
"The End."

299
00:19:17,861 --> 00:19:24,260
That's what I imagine happened behind the camera.

300
00:19:24,261 --> 00:19:28,360
It's true that your story explains

301
00:19:28,361 --> 00:19:33,060
