so we went to Grand Light with Sumire where Nagisa lived.

336
00:22:56,061 --> 00:22:58,061
Nagisa.

337
00:23:04,161 --> 00:23:06,961
Yuri, you're okay.

338
00:23:08,161 --> 00:23:12,360
Yes. I've been fine this whole time, Nagisa.

339
00:23:12,361 --> 00:23:13,760
I'm so glad.

340
00:23:13,761 --> 00:23:17,461
I had such a long and terrible dream.

